This directory is for Nirvana documentation related
to the usage of the freeware programming application
Crimson Editor.

[crimsoneditor.com]

It is *highly* recommended.

Illarion recommends:
 -SmartFTP <www.smartftp.com>
 -FileZilla <filezilla.sourceforge.net>

Directory contents:
README: This file, idiot.
nirvCode.c : Template code file for Nirv <optional>
nirvStyle.txt - Installation instructions for Vertebraker's
                Crimson Editor configuration files.
nirvana.key & nirvana.spc - Follow the friggin' directions in nirvStyle.
